These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, comedy, adventure
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person watching scientific movies and the owner of the frog##7
2. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
3. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | comedy | scientific |
| Pet           | frog  | hedgehog     | chinchilla  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, d&b, soul
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, roller
1. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere between the fan of soul and the person driving the car##7
3. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | dubstep | soul |
| Transport     | car       | roller     | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, cola
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, quad-bike, motorbike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person driving the van##7
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | iced-tea | juice | cola  |
| Transport   | motorbike  | quad-bike  | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, bartender, paramedic
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, disaster, family
1. the manager is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the bartender##7
2. the person watching disaster movies is not the manager##6
3. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | bartender | manager | paramedic     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster    | musical          | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, trance, country
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, jet-ski, subway
1. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the fan of trance##7
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the fan of country##1
3. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | rock      | country     | trance   |
| Transport     | subway | jet-ski | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, techno, d&b
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, argentine, british
1. the turkish is on the left or right of the argentine##3
2. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
3. the fan of techno is on the right of the british##1
4. the fan of techno is somewhere between the british and the fan of funk##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | techno     | funk     |
| Nationality   | british | argentine | turkish |

