.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, mouse, bird
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, swimming, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the person who's sport is surfing##7
3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | bird       | mouse      | snake       |
| Sport   | surfing | weightlifting | swimming |

