1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the accountant##3
2. the person watching epic movies is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the dressmaker##7
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | fisherman | accountant  | dressmaker |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie      | epic | superhero      |

