.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, dancing, rock-climbing
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, fisherman, dancer
1. the dancer is not the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##6
2. the fisherman is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the chef is somewhere between the fisherman and the person who's hobby is dancing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | dancing | rock-climbing | gardening   |
| Job     | dancer    | chef  | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, ice-hockey, rowing
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | tea    | hot-chocolate |
| Sport      | rowing | biathlon | ice-hockey |

