.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There 3 different types of food: grapefruit, watermelon, orange
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, action, drama
1. the person watching action movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching epic movies is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person eating grapefruit##7
3. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food          | grapefruit  | orange       | watermelon     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | epic | action |

