2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the fan of classical is somewhere between the fan of disco and the person drinking milk##7
4. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
