2. the person driving the boat is the person eating radish##1
3. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the person eating pepper##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food        | radish | peach | pepper |
| Transport   | boat  | bus       | tram      |

